37.000Z","msg":"所有機組人員及船員在機場入境時，強制留下深喉唾液樣本做測試。不過，措施仍有漏洞，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">到內地出席股東會的上市公司董事、在廣東省設有生產線的公司僱員、與履行與政府相關運作的政府人員和符合相關條件的仲裁員等<span class=\"blue\">仍獲豁免接受病毒測試</span></span></strong></span>，未能杜絕相關輸入個案風險。<br />\n許樹昌亦指，第三波爆發與早前放寬邊境措施，容許特定人士豁免檢疫有關，&ldquo;機組人員同海員，或者公務、商務人士，以往這些人在香港都不需要留樣本，而他們很可能將病毒帶入社區&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"012899864abbe80ec9d2618a64ff09879a45dae6","tid":2308642,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:42:42.000Z","msg":"泛民明明已經。。"},{"pid":"d5b6063c5783cdd8a743a7259fbac96733b7d4f4","tid":2308642,"uid":291557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8222c29d121fad816b310565cbb31c969cdd6f3","tid":2308642,"uid":333143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"信正苦 無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de34c3587ac18455ce887c6323453b2f4ee72879","tid":2308642,"uid":256331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184401569735b4932aaede53bdacecd107a54da","tid":2308642,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"跳舞班人播毒咁勁"},{"pid":"485a79f97c9dbee620aa9ce83fdf5351cde80d23","tid":2308642,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<br />\n成7m 人得個少少100 算甚麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33ebddd4452afe9d373576defa1f0aa1d8b2e00","tid":2308642,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627e1b29a05cd3b381cf8484f35d2cf590230b25","tid":2308642,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:25:52.000Z","msg